snippet.title: What if Newspapers Disappeared? | #aumsum #kids #science #education #children
snippet.description:
What if Newspapers Disappeared?
Firstly, if newspapers disappeared, many people may start missing their daily morning routine of reading a newspaper while having a hot cup of tea or coffee.
Secondly, if newspapers disappeared, millions of people may remain unaware of important events happening in their city or in the world.
Thirdly, if newspapers disappeared, consumption of news related apps or websites may skyrocket.
Fourthly, if newspapers disappeared, people who pay but never actually read a newspaper will start saving some money.
Fifthly, if newspapers disappeared, people who are used to reading news on their smart-phones or computers may not even notice their disappearance.
Lastly, if newspapers disappeared, soybean farmers will be disappointed as soy ink is commonly used while printing newspaper.
On the flip side, if newspapers disappeared, millions of trees will be saved from the axe.
